name: Walnut Sheet Cake Recipe | Shireen Anwar | Masala TV
ingredients: Ingredients for Walnut Sheet Cake Recipe: Flour 2 cups Sugar 2 cups Baking Soda 1 tsp heaped Salt ½ tsp Butter milk ½ cup Eggs 2 Butter 8 oz Water 1 cup Cocoa 5 tbsp Vanilla 1 tsp Ingredients for Icing: Butter 100 grams Milk 6 tbsp Cocoa 5 tbsp Vanilla 1 tsp Icing sugar 2 ½ to 3 cups Walnut (chopped) 1 cup
instructions: Mix 2 cups flour, one tsp baking soda, half tsp salt, and 2 cup sugar in a bowl. Add in half cup butter milk, vanilla essence and 2 eggs (if small add 3 eggs) and beat well. Then melt 200 grams butter in a sauce pan add 5 tbsp coco, and 1 cup water. Heat till everything is melted, pour in the mixture of dry ingredients, and butter milk. Pour the better in a greased and lined Swiss roll tray 10x 15 and bake on 180 degrees for 20 min. Remove cool spread with frosting. In a sauce pan, put all together melt for 2 â 3 min. Add 1 cup walnuts spread all over the cake, chill and serve.
